node.text: Fred Stoker founded the family business in West Tennessee in the early 1900's. Stoker's pioneered the mail-order tobacco market selling premium chewing tobacco in bulk. Today #BobbyStoker leads the family business continuing in the traditions of his father with the same home-grown American entrepreneurship.
